        <h1
          class="text-3xl leading-none tracking-tight font-extrabold sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
        >
          <span class="block xl:inline">
            No matter how busy you get, stay organized <span class="text-brand">with Homebox</span>
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl md:max-w-3xl"
        >
          An elegant scheduling, client management, invoicing, and payment collection product for home service providers.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start items-center md:mt-8 text-base font-bold">
          <a
            href="/signup/user"
            class="flex justify-center text-semibold bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-150 border border-neutral-150 rounded-full px-5 py-2 text-neutral-700 active:ring-2 active:ring-offset-2 active:ring-neutral-150"
            style="min-width: 120px"
          >
            Get a demo
          </a>
          <a
            href="/signup/user"
            class="flex justify-center border border-brand-outline rounded-full px-5 py-2 text-white bg-brand hover:bg-brand-outline active:ring-2 active:ring-offset-2 active:ring-brand-outline"
            style="min-width: 120px"
          >
            Sign up
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-6 text-center sm:max-w-3xl md:px-16 md:max-w-screen-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-sm md:text-base font-semibold tracking-wider text-brand uppercase">
        MANAGE SIMPLER AND FASTER
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">
        Everything you need to organize your business
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-prose font-normal mx-auto text-xl text-neutral-700">
        Create an account now to see how easily you can improve management of your services, invoicing and payment collection.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="grid gap-8 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/card-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Accept payments
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Take credit card and bank payments, offer instant financing to customers, track payments, and get paid faster.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/calendar-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Simple scheduling
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Easily set up new and recurring jobs, organize your calendar, notify technicians, and manage job details.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/invoice-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Invoicing
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Make invoicing a snap with one-click digital invoicing, auto reminders to customers, and an integration with QuickBooks.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/graph-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Analytics and reporting
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Gain real-time insights into your business performance with our analytics and reporting tools.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/truck-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Team management
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Onboard and manage your team of service workers with our easy-to-use dashboard.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="rounded-full bg-light-blue-100 inline-flex items-center justify-center p-6">
              <img class="h-6 w-6" src="/images/landing/thumbs-up-icon.svg" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
              Happy customers
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-neutral-700">
              Keep your clients informed and satisfied with our communication tools and appointment reminders.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- This example requires Tailwind CSS v2.0+ -->
